<h1>Ably Presence Example</h1>

<p>In this example, we demonstrate simply how to be "present" on a channel and subscribe to presence events. See <a href="https://www.ably.io/documentation/realtime/presence">our Realtime Presence documentation</a> for more details.

<div class="row">
  <input id="enter" type="submit" value="Enter channel (be present)">
</div>

<div class="row">
  <input id="leave" type="submit" value="Leave channel">
</div>

<ul class="row" id="presence-status"></ul>
